The,LimeSpot,personalization,engine,delivers,customized,content,based,on,user,behavior,and,demographics,The,Personalizer,API,is,RESTful,and,uses,JSON,for,PUT,POST,requests,and,responses,An,API,Token,is,used,for,authentication,By,logging,user,activities,the,API,generates,behavior,based,recommendations,such,as,top,picks,related,trending,recent,views,or,popular,Add,user,demographics,interests,or,data,about,your,application,s,content,to,increase,the,engine,s,results,See,the,extensive,API,docs,for,more,information,and,to,get,started,developing,with,LimeSpot